eb.archive.org/web/20180429154548/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Jn/ch_20">20</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180429154548/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Jn/ch_21" class="active">21</a> 				</div>
